data.text:
2002

1 hr 32 mins

Horror, Suspense

R

Watchlist

Where to Watch

A psychopath (Patsy Kensit) stalks a psychiatrist (Patrick Muldoon) whom she believes to be the reincarnation of Jack the Ripper, and her lover in a previous life. Miller: Damian Chapa. Carly: Amy Locane. Jenny: Amy Huberman. Teresa: Aimee O'Sullivan. Directed by John Hough. Also known as "Hell's Gate."
